I can spend it with you.

128
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,719
- Really?
- Yes.

129
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:34,792
We had a party at the post
office, so I had to.

130
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:38,988
So you're here
and I can go?

131
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:42,439
Why go away? It's your day off.

132
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:46,396
They brought a gorilla and show him.
