Alright, then.

157
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:55,117
So the problem of
free time has been solved.

158
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,717
It's that simple.

159
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:04,836
- What's simple?
- The problem of free time.

160
