Yeah, was passing by,
and thought why not go in?

168
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:33,032
I remember when I was a kid...

169
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:37,596
It must be expensive
to keep them here.

170
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:41,118
How much does he gobble in a day?

171
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:43,670
- Who?
- Say, a gorilla.

172
00:13:44,040 --> 00:13:45,393
Who knows?

173
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:50,313
If it were unprofitable,
they wouldn't keep them.

174
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:52,875
There must be some interest, right?

175
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:57,190
That's right, but you're
overlooking the process of cognition.

176
00:13:57,360 --> 00:14:02,115
Not all come because they have nothing
to do, they want to cognize something.

177
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,236
Come on!

178
