A gorilla?
Some shit!

180
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:13,473
I'll go and report on you now.

181
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:18,998
What? Are you surprised?
But I should have.

182
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:43,833
All right, I drink two, you - one,
you owe me a pail.

183
00:14:45,040 --> 00:14:47,998
I drink three, you - one, then 3 pails.
Let's get going.

184
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,592
You're spilling some.

185
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:00,476
That's it.

186
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:02,113
You can't drink.

187
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,395
Two pails.

188
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:09,597
Help!

189
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:19,869
What is it?

190
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,999
I wanted to ask you.

191
00:16:22,560 --> 00:16:25,438
I didn't get it alright.
Were you really?

192
00:16:25,640 --> 00:16:26,868
What really?

193
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:28,833
Going to snitch.

194
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:34,277
No, of course I wasn't . But I ought
to knock some sense into your head.

195
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,395
Come on.

196
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:42,389
Please.

197
00:16:46,640 --> 00:16:51,998
You see, I got nothing
against people drinking.

198
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:58,275
But there is an intelligent
organization of people.

199
00:16:58,440 --> 00:17:02,399
Generally, this organization
is called the state.

200
