Imagine that everybody in
the state would begin drinking.

201
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:09,357
I'm not doing it at working time,
only on my day off.

202
00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:12,637
That's what we should talk about.

203
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:16,110
What is it - the day off?

204
00:17:17,040 --> 00:17:21,636
Suppose we are
putting up some...

205
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:27,034
say, we're mounting
a complex steel construction...

206
