I'm an electrician.

207
00:17:29,520 --> 00:17:32,318
Suppose we're laying down
a complicated circuit.

208
00:17:32,480 --> 00:17:35,313
On weekend we get drunk.
Then get sober.

209
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:39,075
Work for a week.
Then get drunk again.

210
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:40,554
You mean I'm an alcoholic or what?

211
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:44,235
I mean that our state
gives us a day off,

212
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:46,277
even two. And what for?

213
00:17:47,720 --> 00:17:52,589
First, that we would have
a good rest,

214
00:17:52,760 --> 00:17:55,399
and, second, that we wouldn't have
fallen behind in our development.

215
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:58,199
For example, you got a day off
and you don't know what to do with it.

216
00:17:58,360 --> 00:18:01,796
You were passing by the Zoo -
shall I go in!

217
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:05,869
And if you were passing by,
well, I don't know... a pharmacy?

218
00:18:07,120 --> 00:18:08,519
Passing by a pharmacy.

219
00:18:08,760 --> 00:18:12,196
Shall I go in
and buy a purgative, right?

220
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:16,792
You can't drift with
the tide like a log,

221
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:18,951
whichever way it washes me,
I don't care.

222
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:21,317
The state
affords us a free time,

223
