acceleration are we talking about?

231
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:52,752
Not a chance for us on that liner, with
our bloodshot eyes and throwing up...

232
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:54,275
You bastard!

233
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:57,474
You want to make a career
at my expense?

234
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:09,273
Where do you work?

235
00:19:09,600 --> 00:19:12,558
At the repairs shop. He says
I'm throwing up all over.

236
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:13,596
Occupation?

237
00:19:13,800 --> 00:19:16,553
- Was I talking about you?
- About whom, then?

238
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:18,950
- I was developing an idea.
- Quiet.

239
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:20,792
Can you keep silent?

240
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:22,709
What's your occupation?

241
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:23,915
An electrician.

242
00:19:24,080 --> 00:19:27,390
